{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-sheet-js","path":"/sheets/js-packages","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>JavaScript 相关工具的速查表。</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2 id=\"http-server\">http-server</h2>\n<p>http-server 顾名思义是一个 HTTP 服务器工具，用于在本地进行调试。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">$ http-server </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">[</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">dist</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>目标默认为当前文件夹（./）。</p>\n<p>开启 HTTPS 需要用到 OpenSSL：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">$ openssl req -newkey rsa:2048 -new -nodes -x509 -days 3650 -keyout key.pem -out cert.pem</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">$ http-server -S -C cert.pem</span></span></code></pre>","frontmatter":{"title":"JavaScript 相关工具速查表","date":"2020/08/24","category":"信息","tags":["JavaScript","工具"],"keywords":null},"fields":{"modifiedTime":"2021/10/01"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"sheets/js-packages","quarter":"sheets"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2243046057","63159454"]}